items.preText: It's been 50 balls since West Indies last hit a boundary. Shakib goes over the wicket to Carter.
items.text: tossed up on off stump, clipped with the turn to midwicket
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, no run

items.text: flatter length ball on middle and off, clipped to midwicket
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, no run

items.text: length ball close to off stump, angling away. Looks to punch square on the off side, ends up playing slightly inside the line and guiding it finer than he intended, to the left of third man
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, 2 runs

items.text: fullish outside off, driven with a roll of the wrists to backward point
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

items.preText: Extra fielder moves to the off side - two in the ring in the covers now.
items.text: back of a length on off stump, whipped away wide of mid-on
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, 2 runs
Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run
Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run
Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, 2 runs
Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, no run

items.text: tossed up outside off, leans across to try and lap-sweep, misses and is hit on the fron tpoad
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, no run

items.text: flat length ball on off stump, punched back to the bowler
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, no run

items.text: flat again, doesn't spin this time, looks to defend and gets an outside edge into the point region
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, no run

items.text: a touch shorter, goes deep in his crease to dab to the right of short third man
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, 2 runs

items.text: a bit more air on this, swept into the midwicket region
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Carter, 1 run

items.text: given! Back of a length, angling into the stumps, and he's caught on the crease as he looks to work it across the line. Skids on with a bit of inward movement to beat the inside edge. Was that missing leg stump, possibly? No DRS, and Carter doesn't look too happy
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Carter, OUT

dismissal.text: JL Carter lbw b Mustafizur Rahman 3 (15m 14b 0x4 0x6) SR: 21.42

items.preText:
Richard: "The best find for WI before the WC is a player like Shai Hope. He is consistent and plays according to the situation. Adding Gayle and Russel, they are a real threat in the tournament following."

In walks the captain, Jason Holder.
items.text: back of a length, angling away from off stump, and Holder, looking to jab away from the body without moving his feet, is beaten first ball
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Holder, no run

items.text: back of a length outside off, lets it come on and dabs to third man. That brings up West Indies' 100
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Holder, 1 run

items.text: fullish outside off, driven firmly but can't beat extra-cover
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

items.text: overpitched, and he misses out, drives straight to extra-cover once more
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

items.text: back of a length, angling away from off stump, punched to that man at extra-cover once more
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Hope, no run

items.text: full on middle stump, clipped to straight midwicket
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, no run

items.text: flat, back of a length, slides on down the leg side. Looks to flick and misses, is hit on the pad
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, no run

items.text: flighted ball drifting in towards off stump, blocked back to the bowler
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, no run

items.text: again Holder plays for turn when there's none. Slider drifting down leg, gets forward to flick and is hit on the front pad
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, no run

items.text: full close to off stump, defended into the covers
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Holder, no run
